OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA cloudy
OL,6,Fevening with showers, perhaps heavy at
OL,7,Ftimes. These becoming more frequent by
OL,8,Fmidnight and merging to give more
OL,9,Fwidespread rain by Saturday morning.
OL,10,FSome brisk winds also developing along
OL,11,Fthe coast.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FRain, heavy at times through
OL,14,Fthe morning, gradually eases away
OL,15,Fsouth and east through the afternoon.
OL,16,FSome brighter or sunny spells
OL,17,Ffollowing, but feeling rather chilly,
OL,18,Fespecially in the breeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
